General Help:

LMB to attack/use, E to open inventory, and R to open crafting.
H to display help menu/item description.
SPACE to hold/craft an item, and Q to put away held item.
SCROLL to move inventory/crafting menu selector, and SHIFT + SCROLL to jump through favorites or change recipe category.
F to favorite/unfavorite an item.
